Package ru.postgrespro.perf.pgmicrobench.statanalyzer.multimodality

Class DiagnosticsBin

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.postgrespro.perf.pgmicrobench.statanalyzer.multimodality.DiagnosticsBin
  • public class DiagnosticsBin
extends Object
    Class representing diagnostic bin for analyzing density histograms. Each DiagnosticsBin wraps DensityHistogramBin and tracks additional diagnostic properties such as water level, mode, lowland and peak status.
